{"type":"message","id":"dc9945d3","parentId":"8ee90075","timestamp":"2026-02-25T00:00:00.156Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:c0707b44-d291-4e3b-8399-91bbb500d041 Daily 8AM Report] Generate and send a comprehensive daily report for yesterday. Read memory/daily/YYYY-MM-DD.md, diary/YYYY-MM-DD.md, and morning chat logs from yesterday. Include: 1) Key activities and work completed, 2) Important learnings and insights, 3) Progress on projects, 4) Notable conversations or decisions, 5) Plans or next steps mentioned. ALSO: Check OpenClaw PR #24218 status using 'gh pr view 24218 --repo openclaw/openclaw' and include any updates in the report. Send the complete report to Feishu.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, February 25th, 2026 — 8:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1771977600151}}
